HEBCPF Third-Party Notices
==========================

HEBCPF depends on MATPOWER at runtime. The solver calls MATPOWER functions
including, but not limited to, `runpf`, `makeYbus`, `idx_bus`, and `idx_brch`.
MATPOWER must be installed separately and added to the MATLAB path.

MATPOWER:
  https://matpower.org
  https://github.com/MATPOWER/matpower

MATPOWER is distributed by its authors under its own license terms. Users
should consult the MATPOWER distribution for the authoritative license text.

