MATPOWER makeYbus
-----------------

Earlier internal copies of this project included a local `makeY.m` based on
MATPOWER's `makeYbus.m`. That local copy has been removed. Current HEBCPF
code calls MATPOWER's installed `makeYbus` directly instead of redistributing
the function.

MEX Binaries
------------

The MEX releases include precompiled Windows 64-bit MATLAB `.mexw64` files for
selected hot-path routines. They are provided for convenience. Users on other
platforms should rebuild them with `build_mex` and MATLAB Coder, or use one of
the pure MATLAB releases.

